View.Name: HashConfigurationView
View.SQL: CREATE VIEW HashConfigurationView (ID, IsInitialized, BatchSize, Salt) AS SELECT HashConfiguration.ID, HashConfiguration.IsInitialized, HashConfiguration.BatchSize, CONVERT(VARBINARY(MAX), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, HashConfiguration.[Salt])) Salt FROM HashConfiguration [HashConfiguration]

View.Name: HL7MessageView
View.SQL: create view HL7MessageView (Guid, WhenCreated, WhenProcessed, Status, PatientID, MessageType, MessageControlIdentifier, Message) as select HL7Message.Guid, HL7Message.WhenCreated, HL7Message.WhenProcessed, HL7Message.Status, HL7Message.PatientID, HL7Message.MessageType, HL7Message.MessageControlIdentifier, CONVERT(VARCHAR(MAX), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, HL7Message.[Message])) Message from HL7Message [HL7Message]

View.Name: LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetailView
View.SQL: create view LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetailView as select [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].Guid, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].LegacyInterfaceHistoryID, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].Code, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].Description, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].SeverityLevel, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].WhenOccurred, CONVERT(VARCHAR(MAX), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].[Body])) Body, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].LineNumber, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].LegacyExceptionDefinitionID, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].MessageDump, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].DataInterfaceID, [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail].PatientMessageID from LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail [LegacyInterfaceHistoryDetail]

View.Name: PatientMessageView
View.SQL: create view PatientMessageView as SELECT [PatientMessage].PatientMessageID, CONVERT(VARCHAR(max), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [PatientMessage].[Body])) Body, [PatientMessage]. PatientMessageClassificationCode, [PatientMessage].MessageControlIdentifier, [PatientMessage].PatientID, [PatientMessage].[SendingApplication], CONVERT(VARCHAR(32), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [PatientMessage].[SendingFacillity])) SendingFacillity, [PatientMessage].WhenCreated FROM dbo.PatientMessage

View.Name: PatientView
View.SQL: create view dbo.PatientView as select [Patient].ID, CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[FirstName])) FirstName, CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[LastName])) LastName, CONVERT(VARCHAR(128), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[MiddleName])) MiddleName, CONVERT(TINYINT, CONVERT(VARCHAR, DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[Gender]))) Gender, CONVERT(TINYINT, CONVERT(VARCHAR, DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[Status]))) Status, CONVERT(DATE, CONVERT(VARCHAR, DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[BirthDate]))) BirthDate, CONVERT(VARCHAR(64), DecryptByKeyAutoCert(CERT_ID('PatientEncryptionCertificate'), NULL, [Patient].[MedicalRecordNumber])) MedicalRecordNumber, [MedicalRecordHash] from Patient [Patient]
